Subject: Getting rid of annoying beep on laptop

John,

You can put the following line at the very bottom of your
/etc/rc.d/rc.local file:

	setterm -blength 0

You will probably also want to put the following line in your .bashrc or
.cshrc file (depending on whether you use bash or csh as your shell):
	
	xset b off

Neal


